# ChatPilot 🧠💬

A Django-powered AI chat app with login, chat history, and OpenRouter integration.

## Features
- 🔐 Secure login
- 💬 AI chat interface
- 📜 Chat history tracking
- 🖼️ Bootstrap styling

## Getting Started
```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/chatpilot.git
cd chatpilot
python manage.py migrate
python manage.py runserver
